casebody.data:
Monday, February 24, 1997

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

97-377. State ex rel. Montgomery v. Marcelain.

In Mandamus and Prohibition. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for writs of mandamus and prohibition and was considered in a manner prescribed by law. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed, effective February 21, 1997.

Douglas, J., would defer consideration until the response of respondents is received.
